                        <interp inst="t18351026-2146-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 24.—
<rs id="t18351026-2146-punishment-27" type="punishmentDescription">
